名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8sF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=4fa522b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1823c35147c45bb564882b688f6453d46da87cb","tid":1517072,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4590c9410caa70a523180c3e8b56c7c1b9b1c00a","tid":1517072,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1ce58499da5227de54f6a2b20395641b160c2b","tid":1517072,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cab75ebdca8ce8dd35d2312d535443664edcb9d","tid":1517072,"uid":222970,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e2fbb88d6a1ec3afa22c24f1802b0362ecab0069","tid":1517072,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T20:43:07.000Z","msg":"幾廿萬一枝槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T20:56:47.000Z","msg":"發夢見到deepweb唔洗咁貴 3000已經有交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi